The information presented is neither an offer to sell nor the solicitation of an offer to buy any security, which can be made only by prospectus or official documents. Such documents explain all the implications and risks of the respective offering of the securities to which it relates including risks, fees and expenses. Prospectuses and/or offering documents should be read carefully prior to investing.
Alternative investments are highly speculative and not suitable for all investors. Alternative asset classes are typically more volatile than investments in other asset classes such as equities and fixed income. This volatility may result in significant price fluctuation and loss of some or all principal invested. Additionally, alternative investments may be illiquid and in some cases can create tax liabilities. There is no assurance that the stated objectives will be met. Several of these programs available are for sophisticated investors only or may be limited to established accredited clients.
Product availability changes from time to time. Contact us directly if you have questions about specific products.
Entities listed here outside of AIG companies are not affiliated with FSC Securities Corporation.

