Overview
The Direxion Indexed Commodity Strategy Fund seeks investment results, before fees and expenses, that track the performance of the Auspice Broad Commodity ER Index, (ABCERI), a long/flat index, that can be exposed to up to 12 commodities (long) or cash (flat).



 
DXCIX
DXCTX
DXSCX


Overall Morningstar Rating1






Out of 112 Commodity Broad basket funds as of 6/30/2017. An investments overall Morningstar Rating, based on its risk adjusted return, is a weighted average of its applicable 3-, 5-, and 10-year Ratings. See disclosures below for details.

